author: wn.com
title: Hockey to make final speech to Parliament before resignation
text: The former Treasurer Joe Hockey has told his colleagues that he will give his final speech to Parliament tomorrow and then resign. It means there will be a by-election for the safe Liberal seat Mr Hockey has held for almost 20 years. But there are signs the new leadership team is making progress with some of the budget measures that Mr Hockey announced in 2014. ...
